Description:
You are inside the hatch, here you can see what at first glance seems to be a normal basement, but at the end of the room you can see a door with three pigmen keeping watch.
				
They are new to this place and they don't seem very excited about having to stand guard, in fact one of them is lying down and almost asleep.
				
The other two don't seem to be very smart either but they could raise the alarm depending on how you approach.
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
